<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Pybind11 on miyan的博客</title><link>https://miyan.site/tags/pybind11/</link><description>Recent content in Pybind11 on miyan的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 10 May 2025 18:26:21 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://miyan.site/tags/pybind11/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>pybind11使用(2) 编写C++类并导出为pyd</title><link>https://miyan.site/p/pybind11%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A82-%E7%BC%96%E5%86%99c-%E7%B1%BB%E5%B9%B6%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%BApyd/</link><pubDate>Fri, 02 Sep 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://miyan.site/p/pybind11%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A82-%E7%BC%96%E5%86%99c-%E7%B1%BB%E5%B9%B6%E5%AF%BC%E5%87%BA%E4%B8%BApyd/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="导出的坑">导出的坑
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="dynamic-module-does-not-define-module-export-function">dynamic module does not define module export function
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>这是由于导出的包名不一致导致的，需要保证
cmake的project名称&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-cmake" data-lang="cmake">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">project&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;haha&amp;#34;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">LANGUAGES&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">CXX&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c"># &amp;lt;-- haha
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">find_package&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">Python&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">3.8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">EXACT&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">COMPONENTS&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">Interpreter&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">Development&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">REQUIRED&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">find_package&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">pybind11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">REQUIRED&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">pybind11_add_module&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">${&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">PROJECT_NAME&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">src/main.cpp&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>与
main.cpp里的PYBIND11_MODULE&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c++" data-lang="c++">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">PYBIND11_MODULE&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">haha&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">m&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// &amp;lt;-- haha
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">m&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">doc&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;haha c++ wrapper&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>名称一致&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="回调函数">回调函数
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>我们可以在cpp里定义一个回调函数，然后python定义一个函数传到c++里，从而从c++取到数据&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c++" data-lang="c++">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// c++
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="k">using&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">PyCallback&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">std&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">function&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">void&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">pybind11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">bytearray&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">Haha&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">public&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="kt">void&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">setCallback&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">PyCallback&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">pyfn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">m_pyfn&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">pyfn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="kt">void&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nf">onDataAvaiable&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">char&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">*&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">buf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">len&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">m_pyfn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">pybind11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">bytearray&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">buf&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">len&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">));&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">private&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">PyCallback&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">m_pyfn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">};&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">PYBIND11_MODULE&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">haha&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">m&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">pybind11&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">class_&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Haha&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">m&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;Haha&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">def&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">&amp;#34;setCallback&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Haha&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">::&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">setCallback&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">);&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">// python
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">def&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">fn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">data&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">print&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">data&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">hahaInstance&lt;/span> &lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">m&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">Haha&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">()&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">hahaInstance&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">.&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">setCallback&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">fn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">while&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nl">True&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="c1">// 阻塞保证hahaInstance一直运行，不断调用callback
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h4 id="报错some-automatic-conversions-are-optional-and-require-extra-headers-to-be-included-when-compiling-your-pybind11-module">报错：Some automatic conversions are optional and require extra headers to be included when compiling your pybind11 module
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>这是由于使用了c++的function但是导出的时候未&lt;code>#include &amp;lt;pybind11/functional.h&amp;gt;&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="报错-dll-load-failed-while-importing-xxx">报错: DLL load failed while importing xxx
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>这是由于c++库引用了某个dll，但是没和pyd放到同一路径下，python import 的时候自然找不到对应的dll了&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="执行python传入的回调函数时直接crash">执行python传入的回调函数时直接crash
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>cpp里不能把PyCallback写成引用&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-c++" data-lang="c++">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">class&lt;/span> &lt;span class="nc">Haha&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="k">private&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">:&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="n">PyCallback&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;amp;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">m_pyfn&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="c1">// &amp;lt;-- 不能写引用
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="c1">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">};&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div></description></item><item><title>pybind11使用(1) cmake + vcpkg 环境配置以及一些坑</title><link>https://miyan.site/p/pybind11%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A81-cmake--vcpkg-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%9D%91/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Sep 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://miyan.site/p/pybind11%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A81-cmake--vcpkg-%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E4%BB%A5%E5%8F%8A%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E5%9D%91/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="看似简单的配置流程">看似简单的配置流程
&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>安装 : &lt;code>vcpkg install pybind11&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>
&lt;p>编写 cmake&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-cmake" data-lang="cmake">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">find_package&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">pybind11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">REQUIRED&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">pybind11_add_module&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">${&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">PROJECT_NAME&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">src/main.cpp&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2 id="问题随之而来">问题随之而来
&lt;/h2>&lt;h3 id="build-link--fatal-error-lnk1104-cannot-open-file-optimizedlib">[build] LINK : fatal error LNK1104: cannot open file &amp;lsquo;optimized.lib&amp;rsquo;
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>这个问题在老版vcpkg是存在的，在&lt;a class="link" href="https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg/pull/26239" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>某一版本&lt;/a>修复
而我的vcpkg好久没pull了，不幸的命中了这个问题，看来用vcpkg得及时更新&amp;hellip;&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="无效的函数python_add_library">无效的函数python_add_library
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>由于pybind11在python3.8导出的模块只能给对应的python3.8版本用，导致想用多个python版本跑行不通，因此得多个版本编译，cmake脚本应修改为:&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-cmake" data-lang="cmake">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="nb">find_package&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">Python&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">3.8&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">EXACT&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">COMPONENTS&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">Interpreter&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">Development&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">REQUIRED&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">find_package&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="s">pybind11&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">REQUIRED&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="err">&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nb">pybind11_add_module&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">(&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">${&lt;/span>&lt;span class="nv">PROJECT_NAME&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">}&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s">src/main.cpp&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">)&lt;/span>&lt;span class="err">
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>&lt;strong>这里有个坑，如果写&lt;code>find_package (Python 3.8 EXACT REQUIRED)&lt;/code>而不是&lt;code>find_package (Python 3.8 EXACT COMPONENTS Interpreter Development REQUIRED)&lt;/code>就会提示找不到&lt;code>python_add_library&lt;/code>&lt;/strong>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="python的版本管理">python的版本管理
&lt;/h3>&lt;p>主要有两种方法：&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="手动安装python版本">手动安装python版本
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>下载python并安装，注意要把路径添加到环境变量&lt;/p>
&lt;h4 id="vcpkg的version特性">vcpkg的version特性
&lt;/h4>&lt;p>使用version特性需要开启&lt;a class="link" href="https://vcpkg.io/en/docs/users/versioning.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>vcpkg的mainfest模式&lt;/a>
在CmakeLists.txt的同级目录编写vcpkg.json文件：&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-json" data-lang="json">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;test&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;builtin-baseline&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;c0b6d35a67d2ad358a6ced92b7aad16a7bf17737&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;dependencies&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;python3&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;version&amp;gt;=&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;3.8.3&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">},&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;pybind11&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">],&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;overrides&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">{&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;python3&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">,&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="nt">&amp;#34;version&amp;#34;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">:&lt;/span> &lt;span class="s2">&amp;#34;3.8.3&amp;#34;&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl"> &lt;span class="p">]&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="p">}&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="终于可以愉快使用pybind11啦">终于可以愉快使用pybind11啦
&lt;/h2></description></item></channel></rss>